{"tid":809593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國「一帶一路」MV被指抄襲可口可樂廣告歌","createTime":"2018-09-07T09:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T16:18:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eb0bb13746d0a903e29b1c48df5bba11c4bed4cc","tid":809593,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:57:11.000Z","msg":"中國最近為慶祝「一帶一路倡議」滿5年，推出了一支紀念MV，MV名稱為「我想為世界修一條路」。不過此MV卻遭外媒抓包，其實是盜用可口可樂1971年的廣告歌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpPrnpUK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpPrnpUK.png&h=bbab486d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國的一帶一路MV。（圖擷自愛奇藝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpzbFr9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpzbFr9p.png&h=64c80b76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原版的可樂MV。（圖擷自youtube） <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外媒「Quartz」今天刊出一篇報導，指稱中國盜用（rip off）了美國1971年的可口可樂廣告「Hilltop」的創意，還將它拿來宣傳一帶一路。中國推出的「我想為世界修一條路」MV，不只是使用1971年可口可樂知名廣告歌「我想給這世界買瓶可樂」（I'd like to Buy the World a Coke），MV拍攝手法也很類似。<br />\n<br />\n在原版可樂廣告MV中，鏡頭先是鎖定在一名唱歌的金髮女子身上，之後鏡頭慢慢拉遠，變成一大群人在唱歌。在中國版MV中，一開始鏡頭則是鎖定在一名唱著歌、穿中國傳統服飾的女子身上，之後也是慢慢拉遠，變成一群人唱歌的畫面。只不過中國MV中加入了很多信心喊話，像「世界需要一帶一路」、「一帶一路寄託著我們想大聲說出的希望」等歌詞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2544407\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2544407&d=y3Nr2Xfmn7RCtyCHc53wQWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=01defb15\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2544407&h=b65a2768\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2544407</a>"},{"pid":"8c639d8c1d12aa315dc080d44e9f72d114d31dd2","tid":809593,"uid":31841,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"支那人唔抄野就唔係支那人啦<br />\n冇自由+封閉思想，點有創意呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604c2ee3f610c574efd5df6ddc8e48638940e890","tid":809593,"uid":126305,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"支那：要不是我們抄可口可樂，可口可樂早就完蛋了"},{"pid":"6da75a1a17c3249697c1e597e34d987f38d99175","tid":809593,"uid":28624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"連名都要抄埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fe71e7e8012d833ae7693e9d4a26a0ceeb33ccd","tid":809593,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T11:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f8bc4968db32ed8904c50f353b68c741967233","tid":809593,"uid":91633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T11:07:42.000Z","msg":"世界需要一帶一路係幾唔要臉先講得出口剩 睇文字都搞到我紅都面哂起雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196947473c28db230b10d7be41ce0711b467759b","tid":809593,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:22:51.000Z","msg":"好肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba47f772bed401e77961098b0882014e19b344b6","tid":809593,"uid":109743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5444fb94cfc3ff43c8b345ba92bad3d19cd123b5","tid":809593,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"h